[32m│[0m ## Padding Oracle Analysis Summary                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Based on my testing, I can provide the following comprehensive analysis:     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **detailed_summary**                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I tested for padding oracle vulnerability by comparing server responses when [32m│[0m
