[32m│[0m 1. Original captcha cookie + wrong captcha text                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. Modified captcha cookies (last byte changed) + wrong captcha text         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Valid captcha cookie + wrong captcha text                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Key Findings:**                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **ALL requests returned identical 400 BAD REQUEST errors** with the        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m message "The browser (or proxy) sent a request that this server could not    [32m│[0m
