[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The captcha cookie appears to use authenticated encryption (possibly AES-GCM [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m or similar) which prevents padding oracle attacks, OR the application        [32m│[0m
